data.description:
Nestled in Trails of Fossil Creek, this 2017-built single-story home features a modern open concept design with four bedrooms and two full baths, offering both comfort and privacy. Its spacious living area seamlessly integrates a gorgeous well-equipped kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, a dining space, and a spacious family room. This home is spotless and completely move in ready. It has excellent storage with multiple linen closets, tons of cabinets, a mudroom area, large utility room with space for a freezer, split bedrooms and spacious hallways.  This home also features a water softener-purifier that stays with the home and a whole home surge protector.  The kitchen refrigerator, washer, and dryer are negotiable. The location provides an easy in and out of the neighborhood with easy access to 287 for quick access to shopping and entertainment.
Don't miss out on this gorgeous property!
